    <sectiondef kind="user-defined">
      <header>GPIO pin input/output enable flags</header>
      <description><para>These flags allow configuring a pin as input or output while keeping untouched its complementary configuration.</para>
<para>By instance, if we configure a GPIO pin as an input and pass the flag ESP32_GPIO_PIN_OUT_EN, the driver will not disable the pin&apos;s output buffer. This functionality can be useful to render a pin both an input and output, for diagnose or testing purposes. </para>
</description>
